== Russian ==
'''возлюби́ть''' (vozl'ubít') ''(transitive, perfective)''

=== Word-formation ===
''prefix'' [[воз-]] + ''root'' [[любить]] (see).

=== Verb ===
# ''(poetic)'' to [[come]] to [[love]], to [[fall in love]]

